event.title: Fellowship meeting with Karsten Gerloff (president) and Matija Šuklje (legal coordinator) in Cyberpipe, Ljubljana, Slovenia

body.p: On July 9th, FSFE’s president, Karsten Gerloff will be visiting the Slovenian community. The Slovenian Fellowship meeting, which Karsten and Matija will participate in, will take place on July 9th, starting at 17:00 in Cyberpipe, Gosposvetska 2, SI-1000 Ljubljana.
